platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It's not often we stumble across an app that has the potential to dramatically transform your workflow. But with Shapr 3D, theres no need for a desk, a mouse, or a keyboard. With your iPad and Apple Pencil, you can design complex 3D models. The ability to work offline means youll be able to sketch and design from anywhere.
